data.description: $2,000 selling agent bonus with acceptable offer by 11/6/2023.    Welcome to this Charmer! This gorgeous and renovated 4 bedroom and 2 bathroom home is a must see! The home features fresh paint on the interior and exterior, new vinyl plank floors throughout, new light fixtures , New Windows and blinds throughout (2023), New interior hvac handler (2023), New privacy fence (2023), new two car attached carport (2023), large 10x20 shed/workshop (2023).  The home has a spacious first floor master bedroom that was opened and has an added large walk in closet (2023).  The first floor bathroom has been updated with a new shower, new tile walls and fresh paint. The kitchen features granite countertops and stainless steel appliances (2023).  The master bedroom has a sitting area that opens to the spacious deck for enjoying the privacy fenced backyard.  Enjoy the front porch or side covered patio area if the deck doesn't call your name! The exterior of the home also features new gutters on the back and front of the home (2023). The hot water heater was also updated in 2019. The new windows have a transferable lifetime warranty, the gutters have a transferable leaf guard warranty,  the full sized stackable washer/dryer and over flow fridge will remain.  This home offers upgrades, amenities, and comfort!
